# Infrastructure Services — <%= appName %>

MyCLI-generated service modules for <%= appName %>.

| Service | Command | Path |
|---------|---------|------|
| Cache | `my add cache` | `src/services/cache/` |
| Queue | `my add queue` | `src/services/queue/` |
| Events | `my add events` | `src/services/events/` |
| Mail | `my add mail` | `src/services/mail/` |
| Storage | `my add storage` | `src/services/storage/` |
| Upload | `my add upload` | `src/services/storage/` (upload plugin) |
| Payment | `my add payment` | `src/services/payment/` |

See `docs/<service>.md` for provider-specific configuration.

## Environment

All services append variables to `.env.example`. Copy to `.env` and fill in credentials before use.

## Dependencies

Each `my add <service>` command installs the required npm packages automatically.
